display.shortDescription: Slow preinfusion into non-declining fixed pressure
display.description:
Replicates the extraction characteristics of traditional E61-style Italian espresso machines.

Preinfuses at 4ml/s, followed by a the main extraction at a fixed (non-declining) pressure as defined by the 'Pressure' variable
